objectives.  On Spain, on Spain, it’s really - I mean, we designed now
(inaudible) a road, and it’s in the hands of the government and
the hands of the euro group and the hands of the government of
Spain and the governments of  Europe , of the Euro Area, actually.  STAFF: OK, your neighbor, please.  QUESTION: (OFF-MIKE) Scott Solano, dpa-AFX. Mr. Draghi, do
